# Guardrails: transient runtime state (regenerated every run, cleared by `guardrails run --fresh`).
# This is exactly the set RunReset.Fresh deletes. Committed plan artifacts (guardrails.json,
# tasks/**, preflights/**, guardrails/**, guardrails.baseline, state/seed.json,
# state/guardrails-review.json) stay tracked. See issue #258.
/logs/
/state/run.json
/state/state.json
/state/merge-conflicts.log
/state/rewind-intent.json
/state/captured/
